algorithm: The new algorithm calculates the score for each bin by dividing the remaining capacity of the bin by the square root of the product of the item size and the logarithm of the reciprocal of the item size, and subtracting it from the maximum capacity of the bins.
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = (bins / (np.sqrt(item) * np.log(1/item))) - max_capacity
    return scores
